Two suspected hijackers got more than what they had bargained for when fell into the hands of a blood thirst mob by after a failed carjacking attempt. They followed their victims from the Trade Route Mall in Lenasia South Of Johannesburg ,and at the robot in Mondear one of the 4 suspects got out a Toyota Yaris and pointed a gun at the driver .The victim screamed for help and residents responded ,leading to 2 criminals caught and the other two managed to escape .WATCH VIDEO BELLOW: